title: What the “Tech Probe” Means for Facebook’s Shareholders
text: Facebook, along with several other big tech companies, has become the target of an antitrust investigation. How should investors react?

title: PayPal pulls out of Facebook's global digital currency group
text: PayPal has pulled out of Libra, the Facebook-led effort to build a global digital currency.

title: How Facebook is fundamentally changing how nonprofits get money
text: A 10% increase in the number of likes on organizations’ Facebook pages is associated with a 1% increase in the number of donations they get.
